data.description: Wow! BEAUTIFUL 5 Bedroom/4.5 Bath home with 3 car garage on 1/2 acre lot! This home has so much to offer with almost 3700 sq ft and Open Floor Plan. Kitchen has bright white kitchen cabinets, quartz counters, tile backsplash, SS appliances, huge island with bar, walk in pantry, breakfast area and a formal Dining Room. Spacious Great Room has Beautiful Built-ins, a fireplace with gas logs, and plenty of room to entertain. There is a guest bedroom with full bath on the main floor. Office has a closet with extra storage as well. Gorgeous Primary Suite features garden tub, walk-in shower, dual vanities with granite counters, linen closet, and custom walk-in closet. All Bedrooms and Bonus Room have direct access to a bathroom. Outside you will enjoy the expanded patio and fenced in backyard. Convenient Location to shopping, restaurants, #1 ranked Clover Schools, and Lake Wylie!
